{
  "stem": "11274.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I asked in the camp-- you see, this-- we didn't associate with-- with anybody, because you came in at 7 o'clock from-- you stop from work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Three hours, roll call.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By the time you had the little piece of bread, and a bowl of tea, plain tea, and drank it, you'd throw yourself on the thing-- on the plank, and you fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they later on, sometimes, if they had information, they would tell us something-- the block elder, the room elder.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not very often.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they did, that's mostly to the Slovakian girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were a little bit isolated, Danka and I, because we were from Polish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by the way, I did not get-- they have the Star of David on my tattoo.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a tattoo, as you can see the scar from where my number was removed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's right here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This one dot is left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A Jewish doctor removed it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said he didn't want to cut it in crooked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He wanted a straight line, and that-- nobody's going to bother me about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He offered to do it for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and every Jewish girl there, or everybody in camp, all the Jews, had to have a-- had a triangle, half of a Jew star, the triangle.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on their number, too, was a triangle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I didn't have the triangle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't have here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I could have slept with the Gentiles in the other block, if my sister wasn't there and have better life, maybe, or something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I probably wouldn't have done it anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But anyway, this is what it was, then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mengele choosing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that one day, Mengele is choosing.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
